claim.claim-text:
1. A method that executes on a computing device configured to connect to a network via a first access point, the method comprising:
receiving, via a user interface of the computing device, a user request to provision a wireless device for access to the network through the first access point, wherein the first access point is separate from the computing device;
in response to the user request, configuring the computing device as a second access point;
broadcasting a signal from the second access point of the computing device, the signal including an indication that the second access point supports a wireless protected setup protocol;
receiving a connection request from the wireless device via the second access point;
transmitting a network profile to the wireless device according to the wireless protected setup protocol, the network profile being for connection to the network through the first access point; and
deactivating the second access point in response to transmitting the network profile.

13. A method for provisioning a wireless device for connection to a network via a first access point, the method comprising:
connecting a computing device to the network via the first access point using a network profile, the network profile for connecting to the first access point;
receiving, via a user interface of the computing device, a user request to provision the wireless device for connection to the first access point, wherein the first access point is separate from the computing device;
in response to the user request, enabling the computing device to act as a second access point;
broadcasting a signal from the computing device acting as the second access point, the signal including an indication that the second access point supports a wireless protected setup protocol;
receiving at the computing device acting as the second access point a provisioning request from the wireless device;
in response to the provisioning request, transmitting from the computing device acting as the second access point the network profile to the wireless device.
